{"tid":680514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佔領銅鑼灣？ 旺角大媽兵團考慮去銅鑼灣演出","createTime":"2018-05-27T08:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T08:58:16.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba485aafbd11d99874d57e6c9c54e5ab36e23fc9","tid":680514,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會通過要求政府研究終止旺角行人專用區後，周末如常有人在專用區表演。有表演者指，會考慮轉到銅鑼灣等其他地方繼續演出；有市民則認為終止專用區會令旺角失去特色。<br />\n這些歌聲、這些演出可能將會成為絕響。區議會通過研究終止行人專用區後的首個周末依然歌舞昇平。<br />\n葉先生已擺檔6年，每逢周末這裏就是他開「個人演唱會」的場地，知道政府要研究終止這地方都覺得失望。<br />\n周圍「快閃」的他們覺得處處都可以是他們的舞台。<br />\n停下來欣賞的「知音人」都覺得可惜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307182&d=GXNzoZh0xSHPFw8hkR3%2Bf%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=88b1443b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D307182&h=6f03382a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=307182</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd7d64f33abae008fbd2dbd463ae1282ab1f87e","tid":680514,"uid":45760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45555a57206121354b65c1c8968485cc75d86cdc","tid":680514,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"好呀，咪撚黎mk呀屌你班蝗蟲。"},{"pid":"b91e29326694d21fcdb047a1662c14969caf1fd2","tid":680514,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi